Package com.googlecode.kevinarpe.papaya.filesystem.compare

Classes for comparing File references

See:
          Description

Class Summary
FileAbsolutePathLexicographicalComparator Compares two File references using File.getAbsolutePath().
FileLastModifiedOldestToNewestComparator Compares two File references using File.lastModified().
FileNameLexicographicalComparator Compares two File references using File.getName().
FileNameNumericPrefixSmallestToLargestComparator Compares two File references using the numeric prefix of File.getName().
FileSizeSmallestToLargestComparator Compares two File references using File.length().
FileTypeComparator Compares two File references using a list of FileTypes to determine order.
